#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:1
msgid "JSON API"
msgstr "JSON API"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:3
msgid ""
"JSON parsing and serialization helpers are available under `ptool.json` and "
"`p.json`."
msgstr "JSON の解析とシリアライズのヘルパーは `ptool.json` と `p.json` に あります。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:6
msgid "ptool.json.parse"
msgstr "ptool.json.parse"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:8
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:8"
msgid "`v0.3.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.3.0` - Introduced."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:10
msgid "`ptool.json.parse(input)` parses a JSON string into a Lua value."
msgstr "`ptool.json.parse(input)` は JSON 文字列を Lua 値へ解析します。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:12
msgid "`input` (string, required): The JSON text."
msgstr "`input` (string, 必須): JSON テキスト。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:13
msgid "Returns: The parsed Lua value. The root can be any JSON type."
msgstr "戻り値: 解析された Lua 値。ルートはどの JSON 型でもかまいません。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:15
msgid "Type mapping:"
msgstr "型対応:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:17
msgid "JSON object -> Lua table"
msgstr "JSON object -> Lua table"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:18
msgid "JSON array -> Lua sequence table (1-based)"
msgstr "JSON array -> Lua sequence table (1-based)"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:19
msgid "JSON string -> Lua string"
msgstr "JSON string -> Lua string"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:20
msgid "JSON integer that fits in `i64` -> Lua integer"
msgstr "`i64` に収まる JSON integer -> Lua integer"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:21
msgid "Other JSON number -> Lua number"
msgstr "それ以外の JSON number -> Lua number"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:22
msgid "JSON boolean -> Lua boolean"
msgstr "JSON boolean -> Lua boolean"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:23
msgid "JSON null -> Lua `nil`"
msgstr "JSON null -> Lua `nil`"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:25
msgid "Error behavior:"
msgstr "エラー時の挙動:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:27
msgid "An error is raised if `input` is not a string."
msgstr "`input` が文字列でない場合はエラーになります。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:28
msgid ""
"A JSON syntax error raises an error whose message includes the parser detail "
"from `serde_json`."
msgstr "JSON 構文エラーでは、`serde_json` のパーサー詳細を含むメッセージで エラーにな"
"ります。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:31
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:31"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "例:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:41
msgid "ptool.json.stringify"
msgstr "ptool.json.stringify"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:43
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:43"
msgid "`v0.3.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.3.0` - Introduced."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:45
msgid ""
"`ptool.json.stringify(value[, options])` converts a Lua value to a JSON "
"string."
msgstr "`ptool.json.stringify(value[, options])` は Lua 値を JSON 文字列へ変換します"
"。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:47
msgid "`value` (JSON-compatible Lua value, required): The value to encode."
msgstr "`value` (JSON 互換 Lua 値, 必須): エンコードする値。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:48
msgid "`options` (table, optional): Serialization options."
msgstr "`options` (table, 任意): シリアライズオプション。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:49
msgid ""
"`options.pretty` (boolean, optional): When `true`, output pretty-printed "
"JSON. Defaults to `false`."
msgstr ""
"`options.pretty` (boolean, 任意): `true` のとき見やすく整形された JSON を出力"
"します。デフォルトは `false`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:51
msgid "Returns: The encoded JSON string."
msgstr "戻り値: エンコードされた JSON 文字列。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:53
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "挙動:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:55
msgid "Default output is compact JSON with no extra whitespace."
msgstr "デフォルト出力は余分な空白のないコンパクト JSON です。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:56
msgid "Pretty output uses indented multi-line JSON."
msgstr "pretty 出力ではインデント付きの複数行 JSON を使います。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:57
msgid ""
"Values must be JSON-compatible. Functions, threads, userdata, and other non-"
"serializable Lua values raise an error."
msgstr ""
"値は JSON 互換である必要があります。`function`, `thread`, `userdata` などのシ"
"リアライズできない Lua 値はエラーになります。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:60
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:60"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "例:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:72
msgid "Notes:"
msgstr "注意:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:74
msgid ""
"`nil` values inside Lua tables follow `mlua`'s serde conversion behavior and "
"are not preserved as JSON object fields."
msgstr ""
"Lua テーブル内の `nil` 値は `mlua` の serde 変換挙動に従うため、 JSON オブジ"
"ェクトのフィールドとして保持されません。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/json.md:76
msgid ""
"Array/object detection for Lua tables follows `mlua`'s serde conversion "
"rules."
msgstr "Lua テーブルが配列かオブジェクトかの判定は `mlua` の serde 変換ルールに 従い"
"ます。"
